Message Remote Services
-----------------------

This add-on for Mozilla Thunderbird exposes remote services to external processes.
A Java API to communicate with this add-on is available.
An external Java program can use a running instance of Thunderbird installed on the same OS.

This add-on is written in C++, XUL and Javascript.
API is in Java.

Trustedbird/Milimail project
URL: http://www.trustedbird.org
